column4: selectWorkshop
column7: 1) Is there a need to develop a holistic perspective?(on all important dimensions of life)
column8: 2) For you, how important is it to understand the following: a)Yourself (individual)
column9: 3) For you, how important is it to understand the following:  b) Relationships(with family, friends, colleagues etc.)
column10: 4) For you, how important is it to understand the following:  c)Society(and making effort for a society that is just and equitable)
column11: 5)For you, how important is it to understand the following: d)Nature(and making effort for harmony)
column12: 6) The problems that you see around you are due to:  Lack of skills
column13: 7) The problems that you see around you are due to:  Lack of understanding of harmony and inhuman behavior of human beings
column14: 8) The role of education is to develop full human personality (human consciousness) and the competence to live with definite human conduct
column15: 9) Money is the most important thing in human life
column16: 10) The needs of a human being are unlimited
column17: 11) Prosperity means having and collecting more money, property and luxury goods
column18: 12) A human being can be always happy
column19: 13) A human being is basically the body
column20: 14) Relationships are very complicated and cannot be understood in completeness
column21: 15) Technical education is mostly about skills, so human values should be taught by humanities teachers
column22: 16) I can never always trust any human being
column23: 17) The dispute, conflicts and differences among family members cannot be fully resolved
column24: 18) People living in a society cannot have a common goal, and there will always be conflicts in society
column25: 19) Education today is doing a good job
column26: 20) There is struggle for existence in the nature, and only the fittest can survive
column27: 21) Human species is the most developed and it is necessary to exploit natural resources for survival
column28: 22) Universal Human Values can be taught and discussed with preciseness like any other subject
